1. *Probudila* se rano jutros sa osmehom na licu. (She *woke up* early this morning with a smile on her face.)
2. Kada sam je pozvao, već se *probudila*. (When I called her, she had already *woken up*.)
3. Čim se *probudim*, popijem šoljicu kafe. (As soon as I *wake up*, I have a cup of coffee.)
4. Ona me je *probudila* telefonskim pozivom. (She *woke me up* with a phone call.)
5. *Probudio* sam se u sred noći i nisam mogao ponovo da zaspim. (I *woke up* in the middle of the night and couldn't fall back asleep.)
6. Juče sam se *probudio* kasnije nego obično. (Yesterday, I *woke up* later than usual.)
7. Kada se budeš *probudio*, spremićeš doručak. (When you *wake up*, you will make breakfast.)
8. Ona se *probudila* pre nego što je zazvonio alarm. (She *woke up* before the alarm went off.)
9. Buka me je *probudila* iz dubokog sna. (The noise *woke me up* from a deep sleep.)
10. Zbog vrućine sam se često *probuđivao* tokom noći. (Because of the heat, I often *woke up* during the night.)